{"tid":233233,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟有冇人睇得明八卦新聞？","createTime":"2017-05-07T11:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T08:41:23.000Z","uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8d88a1837e485c2769c700e704659e4b2104683","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"成日得閒睇蘋果份娛樂版都唔明個堆代稱係講緊邊個明星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟有冇人睇得明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 唔追星"},{"pid":"27499bbd2eab0e5154d384c2fda7cbecb8870af5","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44d86e36a3b79636daa7add567000637af21eb25","tid":233233,"uid":34841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"反而睇唔明你講乜"},{"pid":"e0df45dbf282ea1c0c778dd0134cdb412a852ae0","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>反而睇唔明你講乜</blockquote><br />\n即係個堆娛樂新聞會用一D名黎代替明星個名<br />\n例如 黑鮑 =阿嬌咁<br />\n但係有好多其他嘅我都唔明係講緊邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想知有冇人會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d730d15cdc74eb81a37be5c49e091a7f6ec30c1","tid":233233,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"其實都係得八姨太果part用花名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"a40a6c189203c5f16d2641a24ce2d7a1171f6b8f","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都係得八姨太果part用花名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n蘋果個 關人隱事 都有，今日講 為食仔 <br />\n但係究竟係邊個我就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知有冇人會知呢堆花名係講緊邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d325a87c552d5464d7b36c2461e87eaf64a95c9","tid":233233,"uid":15345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實都係得八姨太果part用花名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n蘋果個 關人隱事 都有，今日講 為食仔 <br />\n但係究竟係邊個我就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知有冇人會知呢堆花名係講緊邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPost出黎睇下？<br />\n以前高登成日有人轉貼出黎，之後成班人係度鳩估，好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"456bd25b2b2c32336bb1775c247f1bd266f3fc01","tid":233233,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bd5fbb5a06ae8115daae6bec8102291989c4f6","tid":233233,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T16:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525b950876dad138511afef0db6ad1b1e522ee24","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:17:28.000Z","msg":"「為食仔」過去頻頻換畫，出軌飛女玩出火，最後為食仔穿煲，形象插水，連舊愛家人都寸爆佢。<br />\n關仁八到為食仔仲撈得好霉時，舊愛真係對佢仆心仆命，仲出動埋有名爹哋去幫佢。雖然未至於未來外父咁地步，但嗰位前輩真係好關照囡囡男朋友，完全做到愛屋及烏，家庭聚會仲出埋為食仔份錢，認真唔話得。不過為食仔完全係菠蘿雞行為，負心又冇悔意，辣㷫晒人哋爹哋，講明以後唔會同佢合作。"},{"pid":"ab589d0a82b03e84a05bbf39213fb4dbc199810c","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"估下係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我估唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fbb064d658d55c908b7e3cb8ddea97fce647de","tid":233233,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"關仁隱事"},{"pid":"3524f828387bf2141198f8dfac73cee9e79391c9","tid":233233,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:19:04.000Z","msg":"fred"},{"pid":"759d91440128ecf838279c9cca24f48eb17d3978","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"是咪鄭生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯定係咪"},{"pid":"5e60dd688011ef3b772c2c60710e29d5a775c7c7","tid":233233,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:20:25.000Z","msg":"成篇野睇到1999咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68169a0624851867b14db0710b240ca58859ebbf","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成篇野睇到1999咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsor lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4559e1df65d57bbd8ba0e17889b795b93ebcb0","tid":233233,"uid":42108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:21:55.000Z","msg":"「降八度」喺娛圈打滾幾十年，無論當時心情有幾唔好，佢都可以一秒變臉，呢啲絕技，真係少啲功力都俾人話假。<br />\n以降八度嘅知名度好少人唔識，有次佢要去外國工作，本來木無表情，同助手講嘢嗰陣粗聲粗氣，睇落似係因為要早起身，心情唔多好。但轉頭有幾個同胞見到降八度，大大聲嗌佢又手指指，降八度本來扮聽唔到，想擰轉面走，可惜遲咗一步俾同胞截住要求合照。喺舉機一刻，降八度即時笑容滿面，影完立即變黑，偽人真係冇叫錯㗎！<br />\n撰文：關仁<br />\n降八度係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74859e873b4386c63eaae4954f2a178be94f6302","tid":233233,"uid":23764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成篇野睇到1999咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nsor lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我話新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491c2e0499f91bb54e353f23039fd1e7bcd58a73","tid":233233,"uid":81420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「降八度」喺娛圈打滾幾十年，無論當時心情有幾唔好，佢都可以一秒變臉，呢啲絕技，真係少啲功力都俾人話假。<br />\n以降八度嘅知名度好少人唔識，有次佢要去外國工作，本來木無表情，同助手講嘢嗰陣粗聲粗氣，睇落似係因為要早起身，心情唔多好。但轉頭有幾個同胞見到降八度，大大聲嗌佢又手指指，降八度本來扮聽唔到，想擰轉面走，可惜遲咗一步俾同胞截住要求合照。喺舉機一刻，降八度即時笑容滿面，影完立即變黑，偽人真係冇叫錯㗎！<br />\n撰文：關仁<br />\n降八度係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n汪阿蛆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48be371fea0893f4b5ff9ffd505f526941456200","tid":233233,"uid":113631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「降八度」喺娛圈打滾幾十年，無論當時心情有幾唔好，佢都可以一秒變臉，呢啲絕技，真係少啲功力都俾人話假。<br />\n以降八度嘅知名度好少人唔識，有次佢要去外國工作，本來木無表情，同助手講嘢嗰陣粗聲粗氣，睇落似係因為要早起身，心情唔多好。但轉頭有幾個同胞見到降八度，大大聲嗌佢又手指指，降八度本來扮聽唔到，想擰轉面走，可惜遲咗一步俾同胞截住要求合照。喺舉機一刻，降八度即時笑容滿面，影完立即變黑，偽人真係冇叫錯㗎！<br />\n撰文：關仁<br />\n降八度係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張敬_"},{"pid":"0b48922c09c3ea93dbde2ba20c3218d03515b1b6","tid":233233,"uid":36773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T04:54:10.000Z","